        {
            "title": "融創據報將所有境外債轉換股票 股價一度跌逾9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"融創據報將所有境外債轉換股票 股價一度跌逾9%\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ad4f2f2c6e1eb87d3d260e03a5b3f064/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041513510998348.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">融創據報將所有境外債轉換股票 股價一度跌逾9%</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據外媒引述消息報道，融創中國（1918）計劃將所有境外債券轉換為股票。受消息影響，融創股價曾跌逾9%，低見1.38元；暫報1.43元，跌近6%。\n\n</p>\n<p>報道指出，融創正與部份債權人磋商，計劃將所有境外債券轉換為股票，債權人可選擇不同轉換期的強制性可換股債券（CB），並最終轉為股票；一旦落實，將會是內地大型房企首度將所有美元債券轉換為股票。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064062/即時-財經-融創據報將所有境外債轉換股票-股價一度跌逾9",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 14:01:29",
