        {
            "title": "一日2宗墮龜│麗晶花園烏龜墮樓慘死 警列殘酷對待動物案",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"烏龜龜殼全碎，當場慘死。讀者提供\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/aec79dfc144a3ed841d346750b843d4c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041513462596149.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">烏龜龜殼全碎，當場慘死。讀者提供</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日5小時內發生兩宗烏龜墮樓案件，均龜殼爆裂死狀恐怖。九龍灣宏光道80號麗晶花園，今（15日）中午12時37分，有途人報案指在第6座對開，發現一隻15厘米長的烏龜，攤倒地上，龜殼全碎，當場淌血慘死。警員接報到場，經調查後懷疑烏龜由高處墮下，將案列殘酷對待動物處理，事後由清潔工人檢走烏龜屍體待查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196292/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"清潔工人檢走烏龜屍體。讀者提供 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3aae73a6df33abec194b9eab62256e34/2025-04/4_6_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        清潔工人檢走烏龜屍體。讀者提供 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196293/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/36776b4a85d3012878c1abd4a70c09cd/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_131951919.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196294/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7889f96bef2b9d85d27d0893bf40f002/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_131951919_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196295/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"烏龜墮下位置。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a8e3f2d0d2a7a989add4439c528c2f00/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_131951919_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        烏龜墮下位置。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196296/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4e3294bfdac86f7ee2bf6d0cf577300/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_131951919_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196297/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8e06c8f794b07599a7e9c43df385a2f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_131951919_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>今（15日）早上6時49分，秀茂坪曉光街44號富華閣對開，亦有一隻大約4至5吋長的小龜伏屍地上，龜殼爆裂、內臟溢出，懷疑牠被人從高處擲下，死狀恐怖。警方正循殘酷對待動物方向調查案件。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064060/即時-港聞-一日2宗墮龜│麗晶花園烏龜墮樓慘死-警列殘酷對待動物案",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 14:01:30",
