            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "跨省追捕︱奸夫斬殺情人及綠帽夫後潛逃   偷食妻叫醒2女避死劫",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"疑兇(小圖)斬殺情婦及對方丈夫後騎電單車潛逃。抖音@夯土一隅\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c18e152260f00e1ce2ec36a00c9a5972/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041513323362901.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">疑兇(小圖)斬殺情婦及對方丈夫後騎電單車潛逃。抖音@夯土一隅</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>江西九江修水縣有已婚泥水工，疑因感情糾紛，凌晨潛入「出軌」情人的家中，將偷食的人妻及對方丈夫斬死，受害人遇害前及時叫醒熟睡的兩名女兒，其中一女雖身中五刀，仍能及時逃命。疑兇作案後逃入三少目交會的深山，警方目前仍在追緝。\n\n</p><h2>高三女兒中五刀獲救</h2>\n<p>據內媒報道，案發於9日凌晨，48歲水泥工盧某某，潛入修水縣義寧鎮羅橋路一間民房，斬殺已婚情婦及其丈夫。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉斬殺情婦及對方丈夫的疑兇。修水縣公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c9e6c0ba45c9f44c35e774842d3ba7f/2025-04/26556.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉斬殺情婦及對方丈夫的疑兇。修水縣公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"警方公開疑兇資料，呼籲民眾提供線索。修水縣公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af1d155716dd8977526259a6e4f621ef/2025-04/123523.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方公開疑兇資料，呼籲民眾提供線索。修水縣公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"警方動用無人機追捕疑兇。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/552f9bf3f5593a7047e0b0151f183a97/2025-04/256265.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方動用無人機追捕疑兇。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"警方仍在追捕疑兇。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d42150b6b76cf774fd4597be2d0cb3c3/2025-04/1565263.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方仍在追捕疑兇。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女死者去年曾拍片叫人不要出軌。抖音@夯土一隅\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75f8bb3e943482ac3e7ff69190311678/2025-04/4154153.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女死者去年曾拍片叫人不要出軌。抖音@夯土一隅\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"疑兇作案後騎電單車逃離現場。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b2aac84af6759ebd594741dcf2fcbfb1/2025-04/15654162.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        疑兇作案後騎電單車逃離現場。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3444363/CBA%E5%90%8D%E5%B8%A5%E5%8A%89%E7%B6%AD%E5%81%89%E9%81%AD%E7%88%86%E5%81%B7%E5%90%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%BB-%E5%B8%B6%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%89%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E9%82%84%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E5%A6%BB%E5%A5%B3\">CBA名帥劉維偉遭爆偷吃人妻 帶小三出席球隊活動還恐嚇妻女</a>\n</p>\n<p>據死者親屬冷先生稱，他堂哥在廣東打工，返回修水不久被殺害。堂哥和堂嫂有3個孩子。案發時室內除兩名死者外，當有兩名已熟睡的侄女，堂嫂及時叫醒兩女逃生，雖然讀高三的姪女仍被疑兇斬中五刀，但無生命危險。\n\n</p>\n<p>盧某某作案後，騎電單車逃離現場，疑進入了江西、湖南、湖北交會的黃龍山，不排除已逃出江西。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3414143/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B121%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%8D%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3-18%E6%AD%B2%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E6%BB%85%E5%8F%A3\">網傳中山21歲女被前度上門殺害 18歲妹妹同遭滅口</a>\n</p>\n<p>修水縣公安在案發後大舉搜山，並出動無人機協助，但暫未追捕到疑犯，已聯絡湖南、湖北的警方協助。\n\n</p>\n<p>有網民翻出女死者去年的短片，片中，女死者曾勸說其他女性千萬不要出軌。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
