            "title": "新蒲崗景福街單位煮食期間起火 消防救熄無人傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"消防到場救熄火警。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/697fd92866e9ec7e07b667fe4e1c5d2d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041513183780237.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">消防到場救熄火警。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>新蒲崗景福街83-97號昌泰大廈，今（15日）中午12時12分，其中一單位發生火警冒煙，消防接報到場，開喉灌救，迅速將火救熄。火警中無人受傷，毋須疏散，據悉，事發單位煮食時起火，並無可疑。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196228/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救熄火警。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0139962c9f52ca4716476da58158690/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_124011725_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救熄火警。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196229/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事發為昌泰大廈一單位。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e0f9b8f04a540ab7f054ecc57ddb924/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250415_124011725_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"